title.narrative: Food Retail Industry Challenge Fund Procurement of Services

description.narrative: This activity (Food Retail Industry Challenge Fund Procurement of Services) is a component of Food Retail Industry Challenge Fund (FRICH) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £1,171,435. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Business Policy and Administration, Agricultural services. , with the following implementing partners: Nathan Associates. The start date is 01-07-2008 and the end date is 30-04-2014.
